Good try.

00:42:02.694 --> 00:42:04.215 align:middle line:90%
[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:42:04.215 --> 00:42:07.390 align:middle line:84%
OK, so the bath that
you just had also

00:42:07.390 --> 00:42:09.910 align:middle line:90%
is very good for your ankles.

00:42:09.910 --> 00:42:14.300 align:middle line:84%
Because when you hurt them,
your cells had a trauma.

00:42:14.300 --> 00:42:18.090 align:middle line:84%
So all of that gets cleared away
with these medicinal plants.

00:42:18.090 --> 00:42:20.520 align:middle line:84%
So it's not only for
the physical part.

00:42:20.520 --> 00:42:23.290 align:middle line:84%
It is also for the
energetic, for the spiritual,

00:42:23.290 --> 00:42:27.550 align:middle line:84%
for the emotional, for
the psychological part.

00:42:27.550 --> 00:42:33.560 align:middle line:84%
PAM: Before departing, Mother
Irene offered to read my cards.

00:42:33.560 --> 00:42:40.254 align:middle line:84%
In closing she says, it was
necessary for you to leave.

00:42:40.254 --> 00:42:42.594 align:middle line:90%
You've done the right thing.

00:42:42.594 --> 00:42:45.280 align:middle line:90%
You have a great mission.

00:42:45.280 --> 00:42:48.627 align:middle line:84%
The people you left behind could
not grow if you had remained.

00:42:48.627 --> 00:42:52.850 align:middle line:84%
The path that you have
taken is the correct path.

00:42:52.850 --> 00:42:56.350 align:middle line:90%


00:42:56.350 --> 00:42:59.680 align:middle line:84%
I left behind a 15
year relationship

00:42:59.680 --> 00:43:02.690 align:middle line:84%
with a man I thought
I would grow old with,

00:43:02.690 --> 00:43:06.396 align:middle line:84%
and a home that I
thought would be my last.

00:43:06.396 --> 00:43:12.740 align:middle line:84%
I left my friends,
my family, my career.

00:43:12.740 --> 00:43:16.060 align:middle line:84%
And suddenly, in
the past seven days,

00:43:16.060 --> 00:43:19.806 align:middle line:84%
I am told by three different
shamans that I have a mission.

00:43:19.806 --> 00:43:22.700 align:middle line:90%


00:43:22.700 --> 00:43:25.130 align:middle line:84%
I'm a middle aged
woman, now alone.

00:43:25.130 --> 00:43:29.985 align:middle line:90%
What power do I have?

00:43:29.985 --> 00:43:33.230 align:middle line:84%
Puma continued his teachings
as we headed to the Sacred

00:43:33.230 --> 00:43:35.358 align:middle line:90%
Valley and Machu Picchu.

00:43:35.358 --> 00:43:39.170 align:middle line:90%


00:43:39.170 --> 00:43:43.840 align:middle line:84%
Behind here, we
have Machu Picchu.

00:43:43.840 --> 00:43:46.840 align:middle line:10%
We believe that is
perhaps one of the origins

00:43:46.840 --> 00:43:50.210 align:middle line:10%
of the name for Machu Picchu.

00:43:50.210 --> 00:43:53.650 align:middle line:84%
Machu Picchu, as they
say, is to Quechua

00:43:53.650 --> 00:43:56.720 align:middle line:90%
words which means old mountain.

00:43:56.720 --> 00:44:04.190 align:middle line:84%
And perhaps more than that, it
actually means the old bird.

00:44:04.190 --> 00:44:05.720 align:middle line:90%
Machu Picchu.

00:44:05.720 --> 00:44:10.130 align:middle line:84%
Wherever our ancestors
had found sacred temples,

00:44:10.130 --> 00:44:13.260 align:middle line:84%
there had to be
two mountaintops.

00:44:13.260 --> 00:44:15.790 align:middle line:84%
One of the mountaintops
is wayna picchu,

00:44:15.790 --> 00:44:19.350 align:middle line:84%
which is young mountain,
and machu picchu,

00:44:19.350 --> 00:44:20.650 align:middle line:90%
which is the old mountain.

00:44:20.650 --> 00:44:24.900 align:middle line:84%
So in one mountain range, if
they could find two peaks,

00:44:24.900 --> 00:44:27.430 align:middle line:84%
that was for them
a sacred symbol.

00:44:27.430 --> 00:44:29.700 align:middle line:84%
Also, it is believed
that Machu Picchu

00:44:29.700 --> 00:44:33.980 align:middle line:84%
was built as a sacred
altar for Salkantay.

00:44:33.980 --> 00:44:39.440 align:middle line:84%
And Apus Salkantay is a mountain
spirit that is perhaps the most

00:44:39.440 --> 00:44:41.440 align:middle line:90%
important in this region.

00:44:41.440 --> 00:44:46.150 align:middle line:84%
It is hardly accessible,
and in the spiritual sense,

00:44:46.150 --> 00:44:48.120 align:middle line:84%
every medicine man
and medicine woman

00:44:48.120 --> 00:44:50.920 align:middle line:84%
had to journey to
this mountain in order

00:44:50.920 --> 00:44:54.370 align:middle line:84%
to be initiated, in
order to be enlightened.

00:44:54.370 --> 00:44:57.160 align:middle line:84%
And a lot of people
have tried to arrive

00:44:57.160 --> 00:44:59.240 align:middle line:84%
to the summit of this
mountain, and many people

00:44:59.240 --> 00:45:01.320 align:middle line:90%
even haven't returned.

00:45:01.320 --> 00:45:05.640 align:middle line:84%
So we believe that this
mountain is protected.

00:45:05.640 --> 00:45:10.710 align:middle line:84%
That's why we call it salka,
which means wild mountain.

00:45:10.710 --> 00:45:15.650 align:middle line:84%
And a way for our ancestors to
arrive to its actual essence

00:45:15.650 --> 00:45:18.380 align:middle line:84%
of what this
mountain represented

00:45:18.380 --> 00:45:21.510 align:middle line:84%
was for them journeying
to Machu Picchu.

00:45:21.510 --> 00:45:28.210 align:middle line:84%
Because they would take a trail,
what we call an Inca trail,

00:45:28.210 --> 00:45:32.220 align:middle line:84%
for journeying for a long
time, preparing themselves

00:45:32.220 --> 00:45:35.060 align:middle line:84%
in these specific places,
and arriving into Machu

00:45:35.060 --> 00:45:37.140 align:middle line:90%
Picchu in pilgrimage.

00:45:37.140 --> 00:45:42.330 align:middle line:84%
So perhaps this
place was also kept

00:45:42.330 --> 00:45:45.440 align:middle line:84%
in secret because
of that, because

00:45:45.440 --> 00:45:46.630 align:middle line:90%
of being an altar to Salkantay.

00:45:46.630 --> 00:45:49.260 align:middle line:90%


00:45:49.260 --> 00:45:55.130 align:middle line:84%
Also the belief is
that in this place,

00:45:55.130 --> 00:45:57.910 align:middle line:84%
why the Spaniards
never found it,

00:45:57.910 --> 00:46:02.250 align:middle line:84%
not only because the Incas left
it burned, but also because it

00:46:02.250 --> 00:46:07.200 align:middle line:84%
was built in a strategic
point in the mountains

00:46:07.200 --> 00:46:10.710 align:middle line:84%
where it is almost part
of the mountain range.

00:46:10.710 --> 00:46:14.600 align:middle line:84%
And you can only
find it if you're

00:46:14.600 --> 00:46:16.980 align:middle line:84%
coming through the
top of the mountains

00:46:16.980 --> 00:46:19.680 align:middle line:84%
like we are now on
the top of a mountain.

00:46:19.680 --> 00:46:22.650 align:middle line:84%
So if you are down in the
valley near the river,

00:46:22.650 --> 00:46:24.200 align:middle line:84%
it is almost impossible
that you could

00:46:24.200 --> 00:46:26.940 align:middle line:84%
have found it even
if you knew that it

00:46:26.940 --> 00:46:29.390 align:middle line:90%
was going to be around here.

00:46:29.390 --> 00:46:32.190 align:middle line:10%
So the reason why
that was also is

00:46:32.190 --> 00:46:38.760 align:middle line:10%
because it gives you the
feeling that you are a condor.

00:46:38.760 --> 00:46:41.370 align:middle line:84%
That is why you are always
at the top of the mountain.

00:46:41.370 --> 00:46:43.810 align:middle line:84%
That is why you
are always up high.

00:46:43.810 --> 00:46:48.450 align:middle line:84%
And in sometimes of the year,
filled with mist and clouds,

00:46:48.450 --> 00:46:51.400 align:middle line:84%
so it's almost like you're
always in the heavens.

00:46:51.400 --> 00:46:57.140 align:middle line:84%
And in Machu Picchu, the
medicine for this time,

00:46:57.140 --> 00:46:59.680 align:middle line:90%
for this area is feminine.

00:46:59.680 --> 00:47:07.280 align:middle line:84%
Perhaps that is why they
found a priestess mummy that

00:47:07.280 --> 00:47:13.300 align:middle line:84%
was the most important person in
Machu Picchu, and was a woman.

00:47:13.300 --> 00:47:18.590 align:middle line:84%
They found her with all the
ceremonial regalia and the pots

00:47:18.590 --> 00:47:21.750 align:middle line:90%
and instruments for rituals.

00:47:21.750 --> 00:47:27.200 align:middle line:10%
And so we believe, in
the spiritual sense,

00:47:27.200 --> 00:47:30.460 align:middle line:10%
that Machu Picchu was the
sacred temple of the Amazonas

00:47:30.460 --> 00:47:33.690 align:middle line:10%
warriors, which
were women that were

00:47:33.690 --> 00:47:38.460 align:middle line:10%
initiated at the age of 13 as
chosen princesses of the sun.

00:47:38.460 --> 00:47:41.480 align:middle line:84%
And they were trained
physically, spiritually,

00:47:41.480 --> 00:47:46.540 align:middle line:84%
and emotionally to be the
leaders, to be the healers,

00:47:46.540 --> 00:47:50.450 align:middle line:84%
to be the governors, to be the
warriors for the whole Inca

00:47:50.450 --> 00:47:51.930 align:middle line:90%
civilization.

00:47:51.930 --> 00:47:55.240 align:middle line:84%
And here in Machu
Picchu was the place

00:47:55.240 --> 00:47:57.750 align:middle line:84%
where they used to be born,
where they used to be trained,

00:47:57.750 --> 00:47:59.690 align:middle line:90%
where they used to be initiated.

00:47:59.690 --> 00:48:01.980 align:middle line:84%
The Amazonas
warriors, which were

00:48:01.980 --> 00:48:04.530 align:middle line:90%
like the CIA of the Inca times.

00:48:04.530 --> 00:48:07.290 align:middle line:84%
These people were highly
trained in all levels.

00:48:07.290 --> 00:48:10.270 align:middle line:84%
They could put you to sleep
just with their thought

00:48:10.270 --> 00:48:11.660 align:middle line:90%
is what the legends say.

00:48:11.660 --> 00:48:15.610 align:middle line:84%
These people were hatun
munanio, as we call.

00:48:15.610 --> 00:48:20.600 align:middle line:84%
And hatun means big, and
munanio means big love.

00:48:20.600 --> 00:48:23.270 align:middle line:84%
So these people had a
big, big, big, heart.

00:48:23.270 --> 00:48:27.090 align:middle line:84%
If anything they developed
very well was their love.

00:48:27.090 --> 00:48:32.480 align:middle line:84%
And their love for our planet,
their love for their path,

00:48:32.480 --> 00:48:38.000 align:middle line:84%
for the spiritual journey they
had, for the Inca civilization,

00:48:38.000 --> 00:48:39.480 align:middle line:90%
for the father son.

00:48:39.480 --> 00:48:42.230 align:middle line:84%
And so they were like
warriors who would not only

00:48:42.230 --> 00:48:46.680 align:middle line:84%
protect the
civilization, but also

00:48:46.680 --> 00:48:50.110 align:middle line:84%
be the leaders and the
guardians and the witnesses

00:48:50.110 --> 00:48:52.790 align:middle line:84%
of life unfolding
every thousandth

00:48:52.790 --> 00:48:54.740 align:middle line:90%
of a second in their lives.

00:48:54.740 --> 00:48:57.050 align:middle line:90%
Highly powerful princesses.

00:48:57.050 --> 00:49:02.490 align:middle line:84%
And also perhaps we can
say, because of the condor,

00:49:02.490 --> 00:49:04.280 align:middle line:84%
some people arrived
to Machu Picchu

00:49:04.280 --> 00:49:07.120 align:middle line:90%
to leave their physical bodies.

00:49:07.120 --> 00:49:09.890 align:middle line:84%
When they were elders, they
would journey for many years

00:49:09.890 --> 00:49:12.975 align:middle line:84%
to this place, and
they would arrive here.

00:49:12.975 --> 00:49:16.390 align:middle line:84%
And with the help of
perhaps sacred plants

00:49:16.390 --> 00:49:18.880 align:middle line:84%
or some transcending
meditation, they would

00:49:18.880 --> 00:49:21.090 align:middle line:90%
leave their physical body.

00:49:21.090 --> 00:49:24.940 align:middle line:84%
And they would be
afterwards mummified.

00:49:24.940 --> 00:49:28.620 align:middle line:84%
And they were first
placed in a condor altar

00:49:28.620 --> 00:49:34.290 align:middle line:84%
here in Machu Picchu that
is in a flying position.

00:49:34.290 --> 00:49:36.920 align:middle line:90%
And it is facing east.

00:49:36.920 --> 00:49:39.320 align:middle line:84%
The two meanings that
this condor temple has

00:49:39.320 --> 00:49:43.380 align:middle line:84%
is that our ancestors could
be coming from the west

00:49:43.380 --> 00:49:48.060 align:middle line:84%
and arriving and bringing all
the wisdom and all the strength

00:49:48.060 --> 00:49:49.380 align:middle line:90%
for life to continue.

00:49:49.380 --> 00:49:52.640 align:middle line:84%
All the sacred knowledges,
all the sacred formulas

00:49:52.640 --> 00:49:57.330 align:middle line:84%
for architecture, engineering,
and the administration.

00:49:57.330 --> 00:50:02.470 align:middle line:84%
And the other meaning would
be as it's flying to the east,

00:50:02.470 --> 00:50:05.300 align:middle line:84%
taking all these
beings that have

00:50:05.300 --> 00:50:08.560 align:middle line:90%
been mummified to the light.

00:50:08.560 --> 00:50:11.120 align:middle line:84%
Our ancestors used to
come to these terraces,

00:50:11.120 --> 00:50:15.500 align:middle line:84%
and in ceremony they would
receive the first light,

00:50:15.500 --> 00:50:18.090 align:middle line:90%
the first rays of the sun.

00:50:18.090 --> 00:50:23.190 align:middle line:84%
And the sun for our
ancestors represented

00:50:23.190 --> 00:50:28.620 align:middle line:84%
the physical manifestation
of the father of God.

00:50:28.620 --> 00:50:32.250 align:middle line:84%
And now they are
the only beings that

00:50:32.250 --> 00:50:36.920 align:middle line:84%
receive in ceremony the sun
is the llamas that live here.

00:50:36.920 --> 00:50:41.330 align:middle line:84%
And these sacred cameloids for
us represents service of love.

00:50:41.330 --> 00:50:45.620 align:middle line:84%
So for those of us who
will recognize our symbols

00:50:45.620 --> 00:50:48.040 align:middle line:84%
and our sacred
ancient teachings,

00:50:48.040 --> 00:50:52.180 align:middle line:84%
we would realize that whatever
we see these beings receiving

00:50:52.180 --> 00:50:56.880 align:middle line:84%
the sun in this way, we are
reminded that this day is a day

00:50:56.880 --> 00:51:01.250 align:middle line:84%
to serve, that this
day is a day to be

00:51:01.250 --> 00:51:05.260 align:middle line:84%
in absolute and
unconditional service of love

00:51:05.260 --> 00:51:10.070 align:middle line:84%
to all our family,
to all our community.

00:51:10.070 --> 00:51:13.440 align:middle line:84%
Grandfather wold
always say, when

00:51:13.440 --> 00:51:16.860 align:middle line:84%
you're in the sacred temples,
how would you rather be?

00:51:16.860 --> 00:51:19.520 align:middle line:84%
Would you rather be
conscious of the energy?

00:51:19.520 --> 00:51:23.710 align:middle line:84%
Would you rather be conscious
of everything that is happening?

00:51:23.710 --> 00:51:27.530 align:middle line:84%
Or would you like
to be unconscious?

00:51:27.530 --> 00:51:30.100 align:middle line:84%
And I would say,
conscious, grandfather.

00:51:30.100 --> 00:51:30.920 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGH]

00:51:30.920 --> 00:51:33.160 align:middle line:90%
He would say, oh, boy.

00:51:33.160 --> 00:51:35.620 align:middle line:90%
You continue limiting yourself.

00:51:35.620 --> 00:51:40.080 align:middle line:84%
Because when you are conscious,
your mind is in charge,

00:51:40.080 --> 00:51:43.380 align:middle line:84%
and your mind wants to
make sense of everything.

00:51:43.380 --> 00:51:46.365 align:middle line:84%
Wants to understand
it, wants to limit

00:51:46.365 --> 00:51:49.540 align:middle line:90%
it in your complete experience.

00:51:49.540 --> 00:51:53.080 align:middle line:84%
And he would tell
me that when you

00:51:53.080 --> 00:51:57.750 align:middle line:84%
are unconscious
through it all, you are

00:51:57.750 --> 00:52:00.230 align:middle line:90%
completely receiving the magic.

00:52:00.230 --> 00:52:01.920 align:middle line:84%
Because in the
unconscious level,

00:52:01.920 --> 00:52:04.000 align:middle line:90%
all the magic is happening.

00:52:04.000 --> 00:52:06.880 align:middle line:84%
And your mind, instead
of making sense,

00:52:06.880 --> 00:52:09.460 align:middle line:90%
in loses sense of it all.

00:52:09.460 --> 00:52:14.910 align:middle line:84%
And then you are
completely open to receive

00:52:14.910 --> 00:52:17.050 align:middle line:84%
all the energy,
all the magic, all

00:52:17.050 --> 00:52:20.300 align:middle line:90%
the healing that can happen.

00:52:20.300 --> 00:52:23.170 align:middle line:84%
When we talk about
our mountain spirits,

00:52:23.170 --> 00:52:26.110 align:middle line:84%
when we talk about
God, transcends

00:52:26.110 --> 00:52:31.430 align:middle line:90%
gender really, and ourselves.

00:52:31.430 --> 00:52:36.040 align:middle line:10%
In essence, we are
not a man or a woman.

00:52:36.040 --> 00:52:40.530 align:middle line:84%
Our soul, our spirit
transcends that.

00:52:40.530 --> 00:52:43.500 align:middle line:84%
Though we are coming into
this physical temple,

00:52:43.500 --> 00:52:47.970 align:middle line:84%
we are coming into this
sacred planet as a man

00:52:47.970 --> 00:52:50.220 align:middle line:90%
or a woman for a reason.

00:52:50.220 --> 00:52:54.410 align:middle line:84%
And that is why we need to
consider ourselves, our bodies,

00:52:54.410 --> 00:52:56.920 align:middle line:90%
as sacred temples.

00:52:56.920 --> 00:52:59.420 align:middle line:10%
And oftentimes in
most places I have

00:52:59.420 --> 00:53:03.850 align:middle line:10%
heard the weak gender
or the weak sex

00:53:03.850 --> 00:53:05.690 align:middle line:10%
when they are
speaking of a woman.

00:53:05.690 --> 00:53:08.960 align:middle line:84%
And the first thing
I ask them is, well,

00:53:08.960 --> 00:53:12.500 align:middle line:84%
talking about a weak sex or
talking about a weak gender,

00:53:12.500 --> 00:53:15.380 align:middle line:90%
how does a woman give birth?

00:53:15.380 --> 00:53:16.710 align:middle line:90%
Just that even.

00:53:16.710 --> 00:53:23.740 align:middle line:10%
And as a man, would we be able
to support so much pain and so

00:53:23.740 --> 00:53:30.830 align:middle line:10%
much suffering to the point
that a woman can give her life

00:53:30.830 --> 00:53:33.240 align:middle line:10%
for the life of another child?

00:53:33.240 --> 00:53:35.650 align:middle line:10%
And that is the offering
of Mother Earth.

00:53:35.650 --> 00:53:42.430 align:middle line:10%
That is perhaps why when we
talk about pachamama here,

00:53:42.430 --> 00:53:48.080 align:middle line:10%
when a girl is born, the
moment she is a girl at birth,

00:53:48.080 --> 00:53:50.340 align:middle line:10%
she represents Mother Earth.

00:53:50.340 --> 00:53:52.950 align:middle line:84%
And in essence, all women
represent pachamama.

00:53:52.950 --> 00:53:57.110 align:middle line:84%
And that's how sacred
you are as women.

00:53:57.110 --> 00:54:02.350 align:middle line:10%
And in our traditions,
there had to be

00:54:02.350 --> 00:54:05.590 align:middle line:10%
a delicate and a
specific care for all

00:54:05.590 --> 00:54:08.440 align:middle line:10%
the girls that were growing.

00:54:08.440 --> 00:54:10.900 align:middle line:10%
For example, one of the
teachings that I remember

00:54:10.900 --> 00:54:17.980 align:middle line:10%
in our communities is that
when a girl starts being 13,

00:54:17.980 --> 00:54:24.270 align:middle line:10%
they tell her, when you are
in love, be very delicate

00:54:24.270 --> 00:54:28.430 align:middle line:10%
and be very careful when
you're offering yourself

00:54:28.430 --> 00:54:30.890 align:middle line:10%
to another being,
to another person,

00:54:30.890 --> 00:54:33.300 align:middle line:10%
especially if you're
thinking that that person is

00:54:33.300 --> 00:54:35.680 align:middle line:10%
going to be your husband.

00:54:35.680 --> 00:54:40.290 align:middle line:84%
Because he's not going to
grow from your shoulder,

00:54:40.290 --> 00:54:41.930 align:middle line:90%
they would say.

00:54:41.930 --> 00:54:48.260 align:middle line:84%
He will either die or
leave with another woman.

00:54:48.260 --> 00:54:50.460 align:middle line:84%
That is what they tell the
girls in the communities.

00:54:50.460 --> 00:54:54.500 align:middle line:84%
And so a lot of girls are
already being trained that

00:54:54.500 --> 00:54:56.520 align:middle line:84%
life is about
non-attachment, that

00:54:56.520 --> 00:54:57.950 align:middle line:90%
you cannot take for granted.

00:54:57.950 --> 00:55:04.270 align:middle line:84%
And especially in love, which
is where most of the time we get

00:55:04.270 --> 00:55:05.420 align:middle line:90%
hurt.

00:55:05.420 --> 00:55:07.900 align:middle line:84%
And perhaps that is
one of the teachings

00:55:07.900 --> 00:55:10.310 align:middle line:84%
that our ancestors
have left to us.

00:55:10.310 --> 00:55:14.022 align:middle line:84%
Because whenever we
have attachments,

00:55:14.022 --> 00:55:18.400 align:middle line:84%
that is where we get
hit first or most

00:55:18.400 --> 00:55:24.700 align:middle line:84%
when the waves of the energy
of hurt and destruction come.

00:55:24.700 --> 00:55:27.710 align:middle line:84%
They hit us first
in our attachments.

00:55:27.710 --> 00:55:33.050 align:middle line:10%
But when a being is prepared,
when a person is being already

00:55:33.050 --> 00:55:38.450 align:middle line:10%
trained from very early
time, from childhood,

00:55:38.450 --> 00:55:42.180 align:middle line:10%
that life is not to
take for granted,

00:55:42.180 --> 00:55:44.710 align:middle line:10%
that love is not to
take for granted.

00:55:44.710 --> 00:55:47.160 align:middle line:90%
So we can't have attachments.

00:55:47.160 --> 00:55:53.270 align:middle line:84%
And when you realize that
true love liberates you,

00:55:53.270 --> 00:55:59.838 align:middle line:84%
is about liberation and
not about possession,

00:55:59.838 --> 00:56:03.775 align:middle line:84%
then really there's more
harmony and there's more peace.

00:56:03.775 --> 00:56:09.060 align:middle line:10%
Here in the Andes we
have this philosophy

00:56:09.060 --> 00:56:12.040 align:middle line:10%
of the yanantin-masantin.

00:56:12.040 --> 00:56:17.930 align:middle line:84%
Yanantin is a connection,
is a unity of two

00:56:17.930 --> 00:56:20.970 align:middle line:90%
beings that can be together.

00:56:20.970 --> 00:56:25.140 align:middle line:84%
And it can be of
the same gender,

00:56:25.140 --> 00:56:27.000 align:middle line:90%
it can be of opposite genders.

00:56:27.000 --> 00:56:31.300 align:middle line:10%
It is not necessarily
a relationship of love.

00:56:31.300 --> 00:56:34.610 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes it
transcends even that.

00:56:34.610 --> 00:56:39.950 align:middle line:10%
It is a relationship of two
beings who want to be together,

00:56:39.950 --> 00:56:44.310 align:middle line:10%
a sacred power that
together only they

00:56:44.310 --> 00:56:48.250 align:middle line:10%
can be of great service,
great, great service.

00:56:48.250 --> 00:56:50.230 align:middle line:10%
They become allies.

00:56:50.230 --> 00:56:54.420 align:middle line:10%
They become a team that
can be inseparable.

00:56:54.420 --> 00:56:57.820 align:middle line:84%
That yanantin is very,
very powerful to the point

00:56:57.820 --> 00:57:01.600 align:middle line:84%
that in the Andes,
it was considered

00:57:01.600 --> 00:57:07.590 align:middle line:84%
as something more powerful even
than a relationship of love

00:57:07.590 --> 00:57:09.820 align:middle line:90%
or of partners.

00:57:09.820 --> 00:57:12.900 align:middle line:84%
And then the masantin,
yanantin-masantin

00:57:12.900 --> 00:57:16.410 align:middle line:84%
was only applied to
couples, to partners

00:57:16.410 --> 00:57:18.390 align:middle line:84%
who would choose
to walk together

00:57:18.390 --> 00:57:21.040 align:middle line:90%
in life and in their path.

00:57:21.040 --> 00:57:25.930 align:middle line:84%
And it had to be
specifically of a woman

00:57:25.930 --> 00:57:28.300 align:middle line:90%
and a man in yanantin-masantin.

00:57:28.300 --> 00:57:29.170 align:middle line:90%
Why?

00:57:29.170 --> 00:57:30.970 align:middle line:90%
Because of the polarity.

00:57:30.970 --> 00:57:32.700 align:middle line:84%
There had to be
the sacred balance.

00:57:32.700 --> 00:57:35.470 align:middle line:84%
Every medicine man,
every paco, have

00:57:35.470 --> 00:57:39.260 align:middle line:84%
to have its yanantin-masantin in
order to be in complete harmony

00:57:39.260 --> 00:57:41.210 align:middle line:84%
and in complete
balance in the cosmos.

00:57:41.210 --> 00:57:44.380 align:middle line:90%


00:57:44.380 --> 00:57:46.950 align:middle line:84%
PAM: To know that the
leaders of this sacred land

00:57:46.950 --> 00:57:52.456 align:middle line:84%
were all powerful women
gave me newfound strength.

00:57:52.456 --> 00:57:56.840 align:middle line:84%
But I wonder, if,
as a human race

00:57:56.840 --> 00:58:00.870 align:middle line:84%
we are headed towards a major
calamity in the next few years,

00:58:00.870 --> 00:58:04.940 align:middle line:84%
is there any way we can change
course and save our planet?

00:58:04.940 --> 00:58:08.340 align:middle line:84%
And in the process,
ourselves and our families?

00:58:08.340 --> 00:58:11.160 align:middle line:84%
Puma introduced me to the
prophecy of the condor

00:58:11.160 --> 00:58:15.010 align:middle line:84%
and the eagle flying
together, a prophecy that

00:58:15.010 --> 00:58:18.430 align:middle line:90%
is literally written in stone.

00:58:18.430 --> 00:58:20.970 align:middle line:10%
PUMA: There's a whole
oracle of the secret trilogy

00:58:20.970 --> 00:58:23.670 align:middle line:10%
in this altar.

00:58:23.670 --> 00:58:25.940 align:middle line:10%
There's a whole oracle for
the people of the north

00:58:25.940 --> 00:58:27.220 align:middle line:10%
and the people of the south.

00:58:27.220 --> 00:58:29.240 align:middle line:84%
There's a whole oracle
for the eagle people

00:58:29.240 --> 00:58:31.240 align:middle line:90%
and the condor people.

00:58:31.240 --> 00:58:33.350 align:middle line:84%
When you look at
these two birds,

00:58:33.350 --> 00:58:38.240 align:middle line:84%
there is a very, very strong
difference between these two.

00:58:38.240 --> 00:58:40.970 align:middle line:90%
Here is the tails of both.

00:58:40.970 --> 00:58:45.010 align:middle line:84%
The wings of this one
is coming forwards,

00:58:45.010 --> 00:58:48.360 align:middle line:84%
and this one is
coming backwards.

00:58:48.360 --> 00:58:50.830 align:middle line:90%
Two different birds.

00:58:50.830 --> 00:58:55.505 align:middle line:84%
The condor in the Andes, when it
flies, it flies as if hugging.

00:58:55.505 --> 00:58:58.510 align:middle line:84%
And you can see the
wings sort of forwards.

00:58:58.510 --> 00:59:02.020 align:middle line:84%
And the eagle, because
it's a hunting bird,

00:59:02.020 --> 00:59:07.520 align:middle line:84%
it has the wings
backwards like this.

00:59:07.520 --> 00:59:12.790 align:middle line:84%
So this is a condor,
this is an eagle.

00:59:12.790 --> 00:59:15.810 align:middle line:84%
So the prophecy of the condor
and the eagle flying together

00:59:15.810 --> 00:59:17.760 align:middle line:90%
is not so much a prophecy.

00:59:17.760 --> 00:59:20.310 align:middle line:84%
For us, it is an
eternal reality.

00:59:20.310 --> 00:59:23.050 align:middle line:84%
People of the north and the
south in the spiritual level

00:59:23.050 --> 00:59:24.560 align:middle line:90%
are always connected.

00:59:24.560 --> 00:59:28.110 align:middle line:84%
We're always connected, and
will always be connected.

00:59:28.110 --> 00:59:31.950 align:middle line:84%
As people, as humans,
the condor people,

00:59:31.950 --> 00:59:33.870 align:middle line:84%
meaning the people of
the southern hemisphere,

00:59:33.870 --> 00:59:36.600 align:middle line:84%
is this puma,
represented by this puma.

00:59:36.600 --> 00:59:40.280 align:middle line:84%
The puma represents the power
of love, the power of will,

00:59:40.280 --> 00:59:42.100 align:middle line:90%
the power of the heart.

00:59:42.100 --> 00:59:44.930 align:middle line:84%
This puma has the
tail straight up.

00:59:44.930 --> 00:59:47.940 align:middle line:84%
The tail of the puma in
the Andean cosmic vision

00:59:47.940 --> 00:59:51.230 align:middle line:84%
represents all of
its personality.

00:59:51.230 --> 00:59:56.350 align:middle line:84%
So if it has a tail straight
up, it's in a warrior position.

00:59:56.350 --> 00:59:59.670 align:middle line:90%
And the back legs are over here.

00:59:59.670 --> 01:00:02.270 align:middle line:84%
The front legs are
hugging Mother Earth,

01:00:02.270 --> 01:00:05.500 align:middle line:84%
and the head here
kissing, like giving

01:00:05.500 --> 01:00:07.580 align:middle line:90%
the breath to Mother Earth.

01:00:07.580 --> 01:00:10.840 align:middle line:84%
Meaning that the people of the
south, people of the Andes,

01:00:10.840 --> 01:00:16.030 align:middle line:84%
our main actions are focused on
pachamama, on our Mother Earth.

01:00:16.030 --> 01:00:20.240 align:middle line:84%
All our ceremonies, all our
philosophy, all our traditions,

01:00:20.240 --> 01:00:23.700 align:middle line:84%
all our actions
every day are focused

01:00:23.700 --> 01:00:27.610 align:middle line:90%
on pachamama, Mother Earth.

01:00:27.610 --> 01:00:30.210 align:middle line:84%
And we are the guardians
and the stewards

01:00:30.210 --> 01:00:33.830 align:middle line:84%
of all of these ancient
traditions for a reason.

01:00:33.830 --> 01:00:37.195 align:middle line:84%
That is why a lot of
the messages, a lot

01:00:37.195 --> 01:00:41.340 align:middle line:84%
of the sacred knowledge
of the ancient ones

01:00:41.340 --> 01:00:43.930 align:middle line:84%
is yet to be revealed
to the world.

01:00:43.930 --> 01:00:46.650 align:middle line:90%
A lot of it was kept in secret.

01:00:46.650 --> 01:00:51.030 align:middle line:84%
The people of the north,
of the northern hemisphere,

01:00:51.030 --> 01:00:52.980 align:middle line:90%
is this puma.

01:00:52.980 --> 01:00:54.290 align:middle line:90%
It's sleeping.

01:00:54.290 --> 01:00:56.310 align:middle line:90%
Here's the back legs.

01:00:56.310 --> 01:00:58.370 align:middle line:90%
The front legs are crossed.

01:00:58.370 --> 01:01:00.600 align:middle line:90%
Here's the tail.

01:01:00.600 --> 01:01:03.610 align:middle line:84%
Tail around pachamama
means control,

01:01:03.610 --> 01:01:06.070 align:middle line:84%
taking all the resources,
taking everything.

01:01:06.070 --> 01:01:07.990 align:middle line:90%
That is the people of the north.

01:01:07.990 --> 01:01:14.140 align:middle line:84%
It involves all the northern
countries across the equator

01:01:14.140 --> 01:01:16.850 align:middle line:90%
from the northern hemisphere.

01:01:16.850 --> 01:01:21.570 align:middle line:84%
And the southern puma involves
all the southern countries

01:01:21.570 --> 01:01:24.800 align:middle line:90%
below the equator.

01:01:24.800 --> 01:01:33.080 align:middle line:84%
So what is most interesting in
geology is that our Andes being

01:01:33.080 --> 01:01:37.470 align:middle line:84%
tall mountains are very
young, very, very young

01:01:37.470 --> 01:01:42.720 align:middle line:84%
mountains compared to the
Appalachians, to the Rockies,

01:01:42.720 --> 01:01:45.830 align:middle line:84%
to the mountain
ranges in the north.

01:01:45.830 --> 01:01:49.255 align:middle line:84%
Interestingly, these two
pumas have a difference.

01:01:49.255 --> 01:01:53.380 align:middle line:84%
That one is a young puma,
the puma of the south.

01:01:53.380 --> 01:01:56.570 align:middle line:84%
This could be the
father or the mother.

01:01:56.570 --> 01:01:59.240 align:middle line:84%
Because at this level,
they transcend gender.

01:01:59.240 --> 01:02:04.620 align:middle line:84%
When this puma wakes up, being
the mother or the father,

01:02:04.620 --> 01:02:09.370 align:middle line:84%
has the power to bring
change to the world.

01:02:09.370 --> 01:02:12.070 align:middle line:84%
That is what we see,
that is what we know,

01:02:12.070 --> 01:02:13.980 align:middle line:84%
and that is what
our ancestors have

01:02:13.980 --> 01:02:17.050 align:middle line:84%
left as a very clear
message for these times,

01:02:17.050 --> 01:02:18.470 align:middle line:90%
for these generations.

01:02:18.470 --> 01:02:23.060 align:middle line:84%
From pachamama comes
out the serpent,

01:02:23.060 --> 01:02:25.870 align:middle line:84%
the sacred
consciousness, the sacred

01:02:25.870 --> 01:02:28.920 align:middle line:84%
psychological and emotional
temple of our ancestors.

01:02:28.920 --> 01:02:32.100 align:middle line:84%
These are the serpent,
meaning all our philosophies,

01:02:32.100 --> 01:02:34.470 align:middle line:84%
all our practices, all
our ceremonies are just

01:02:34.470 --> 01:02:36.100 align:middle line:90%
coming out of Mother Earth.

01:02:36.100 --> 01:02:39.530 align:middle line:84%
It's coming from pachamama,
meaning all our wisdom

01:02:39.530 --> 01:02:42.340 align:middle line:90%
is rooted in Mother Earth.

01:02:42.340 --> 01:02:46.490 align:middle line:84%
Where the serpent of the
north is coming from where?

01:02:46.490 --> 01:02:47.930 align:middle line:90%
Around here.

01:02:47.930 --> 01:02:52.870 align:middle line:84%
And it's meeting in
this point, two of them.

01:02:52.870 --> 01:02:57.540 align:middle line:84%
Where is the connection to
Mother Earth in the north?

01:02:57.540 --> 01:03:00.530 align:middle line:84%
Perhaps that is why in
the north you always

01:03:00.530 --> 01:03:03.680 align:middle line:84%
connect to great spirit,
to all our relations,

01:03:03.680 --> 01:03:06.580 align:middle line:84%
because your connection
is with the sky.

01:03:06.580 --> 01:03:09.816 align:middle line:84%
And here in the south, our
connection is with pachamama,

01:03:09.816 --> 01:03:11.450 align:middle line:90%
with Mother Earth.

01:03:11.450 --> 01:03:15.380 align:middle line:84%
That is to be the balance,
that is to be the polarity.

01:03:15.380 --> 01:03:19.185 align:middle line:84%
And yet, this representing
the psychological

01:03:19.185 --> 01:03:21.970 align:middle line:84%
and the emotional
temple of our being,

01:03:21.970 --> 01:03:27.170 align:middle line:84%
our consciousness, this serpent
of the north is also bigger

01:03:27.170 --> 01:03:28.840 align:middle line:84%
and the serpent of
the south is smaller.

01:03:28.840 --> 01:03:31.570 align:middle line:90%


01:03:31.570 --> 01:03:33.610 align:middle line:90%
It is not coincidence.

01:03:33.610 --> 01:03:39.270 align:middle line:84%
This one has a very
harmonious curve.

01:03:39.270 --> 01:03:39.980 align:middle line:90%
See?

01:03:39.980 --> 01:03:41.240 align:middle line:90%
Very strong.

01:03:41.240 --> 01:03:43.270 align:middle line:90%
This one has a sharp turn.

01:03:43.270 --> 01:03:45.810 align:middle line:90%


01:03:45.810 --> 01:03:47.020 align:middle line:90%
You see?

01:03:47.020 --> 01:03:54.040 align:middle line:84%
I think this one is pushing
it, which means arrogance.

01:03:54.040 --> 01:03:56.240 align:middle line:84%
There's a lot of
arrogance in the north.

01:03:56.240 --> 01:03:59.810 align:middle line:84%
This is the message
that need to go now.

01:03:59.810 --> 01:04:02.610 align:middle line:84%
Here in the south, where
people can recognize

01:04:02.610 --> 01:04:07.160 align:middle line:84%
to be that Puma, where they
can reclaim their own power

01:04:07.160 --> 01:04:08.850 align:middle line:84%
and be the guardians
and stewards

01:04:08.850 --> 01:04:11.130 align:middle line:90%
of this sacred pachamama.

01:04:11.130 --> 01:04:14.540 align:middle line:84%
Where people in the north can
recognize to be this puma,

01:04:14.540 --> 01:04:17.450 align:middle line:84%
to recognize that they are
sleeping and that they need to

01:04:17.450 --> 01:04:18.740 align:middle line:90%
wake up.

01:04:18.740 --> 01:04:22.110 align:middle line:84%
This is the oracle of
a condor and an eagle.

01:04:22.110 --> 01:04:26.230 align:middle line:84%
This is the oracle for
humanity for these times.

01:04:26.230 --> 01:04:28.710 align:middle line:84%
And the message
is very powerful.

01:04:28.710 --> 01:04:33.450 align:middle line:84%
Puma, you keep saying
that we need to wake up.

01:04:33.450 --> 01:04:35.750 align:middle line:90%
What do you mean?

01:04:35.750 --> 01:04:38.480 align:middle line:90%
You are the puma.

01:04:38.480 --> 01:04:46.170 align:middle line:84%
Waking up represents recognizing
completely who you are,

01:04:46.170 --> 01:04:48.410 align:middle line:84%
that there's a deeper
Pamela inside you

01:04:48.410 --> 01:04:50.268 align:middle line:90%
that needs to wake up.

01:04:50.268 --> 01:04:53.370 align:middle line:84%
That who you are right
now is who you are,

01:04:53.370 --> 01:04:55.020 align:middle line:90%
but there's deeper inside, more.

01:04:55.020 --> 01:04:57.740 align:middle line:90%


01:04:57.740 --> 01:05:02.120 align:middle line:84%
In fact, to know that there's
a puma sleeping inside you,

01:05:02.120 --> 01:05:07.590 align:middle line:84%
that your complete power
of will to change weathers,

01:05:07.590 --> 01:05:10.730 align:middle line:84%
to change your
directions, to change

01:05:10.730 --> 01:05:13.330 align:middle line:84%
the reality of your
family, to change

01:05:13.330 --> 01:05:16.200 align:middle line:84%
the reality of your
community, to change

01:05:16.200 --> 01:05:18.960 align:middle line:84%
the reality of Mother
Earth, that power of will

01:05:18.960 --> 01:05:21.560 align:middle line:90%
is sleeping in you.

01:05:21.560 --> 01:05:26.050 align:middle line:84%
That is what it means when
that puma is sleeping.

01:05:26.050 --> 01:05:29.210 align:middle line:84%
Because you see,
the US or Canada,

01:05:29.210 --> 01:05:30.890 align:middle line:90%
for example, has the power.

01:05:30.890 --> 01:05:33.000 align:middle line:84%
You have the power
because of the technology.

01:05:33.000 --> 01:05:35.530 align:middle line:84%
You have because of
the resources you have,

01:05:35.530 --> 01:05:38.430 align:middle line:84%
because of the financial
possibly you have

01:05:38.430 --> 01:05:39.940 align:middle line:90%
to bring change to the world.

01:05:39.940 --> 01:05:45.750 align:middle line:84%
You're just not doing it because
that will is not woken up yet.

01:05:45.750 --> 01:05:50.120 align:middle line:84%
Once that love, once that
will is completely awake,

01:05:50.120 --> 01:05:51.730 align:middle line:84%
nothing will be
able to stop that.

01:05:51.730 --> 01:05:53.325 align:middle line:90%
It is in the cosmic flow.

01:05:53.325 --> 01:05:58.080 align:middle line:90%


01:05:58.080 --> 01:06:00.180 align:middle line:84%
PAM: Puma remarked
that my injury was

01:06:00.180 --> 01:06:02.896 align:middle line:90%
part of my spiritual healing.

01:06:02.896 --> 01:06:06.260 align:middle line:84%
All I know is that
after 10 days,

01:06:06.260 --> 01:06:09.700 align:middle line:84%
my foot and ankle were
completely healed,

01:06:09.700 --> 01:06:12.450 align:middle line:90%
and I felt lighter.

01:06:12.450 --> 01:06:15.180 align:middle line:84%
But as soon as arrived
back in the States,

01:06:15.180 --> 01:06:18.220 align:middle line:84%
the pain in my foot
and ankle returned.

01:06:18.220 --> 01:06:20.194 align:middle line:84%
So I sought the advice
of a medical doctor.

01:06:20.194 --> 01:06:27.510 align:middle line:90%


01:06:27.510 --> 01:06:29.610 align:middle line:90%
I think he thought I was nuts.

01:06:29.610 --> 01:06:31.610 align:middle line:10%
Your ankle's fine.

01:06:31.610 --> 01:06:33.280 align:middle line:10%
So what do you want from me?

01:06:33.280 --> 01:06:36.850 align:middle line:10%
When I was in Peru, what I
thought was a simple ankle

01:06:36.850 --> 01:06:40.210 align:middle line:10%
sprain, a local shaman
who worked on me

01:06:40.210 --> 01:06:42.390 align:middle line:10%
said it was more serious.

01:06:42.390 --> 01:06:45.030 align:middle line:84%
And I understand
from the translation,

01:06:45.030 --> 01:06:49.470 align:middle line:84%
it was either I-- the
ligaments or the nerves

01:06:49.470 --> 01:06:52.640 align:middle line:84%
in my-- had just
separated from the bone.

01:06:52.640 --> 01:06:55.500 align:middle line:84%
So he pushed the
nerves back into place,

01:06:55.500 --> 01:06:59.536 align:middle line:84%
and then he wrapped my ankle
and foot in a herbal cast,

01:06:59.536 --> 01:07:01.835 align:middle line:84%
uh, I guess to control
the swelling and pain.

01:07:01.835 --> 01:07:05.350 align:middle line:84%
But which it actually did,
because I was able to hike

01:07:05.350 --> 01:07:07.890 align:middle line:90%
Machu Picchu three days later.

01:07:07.890 --> 01:07:10.560 align:middle line:84%
And, um, was it--
by the seventh day,

01:07:10.560 --> 01:07:12.800 align:middle line:84%
I was actually able to
put weight on my foot

01:07:12.800 --> 01:07:14.940 align:middle line:90%
and with no pain.

01:07:14.940 --> 01:07:17.750 align:middle line:84%
But when I arrived back
in the United States,

01:07:17.750 --> 01:07:19.760 align:middle line:90%
the pain returned and increased.

01:07:19.760 --> 01:07:22.600 align:middle line:84%
Well, from what
you told me, maybe

01:07:22.600 --> 01:07:23.960 align:middle line:84%
your quick recovery
was from getting

01:07:23.960 --> 01:07:25.542 align:middle line:90%
immediate medical attention.

01:07:25.542 --> 01:07:26.928 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGH]

01:07:26.928 --> 01:07:28.550 align:middle line:90%
No, that's not true.

01:07:28.550 --> 01:07:31.520 align:middle line:84%
You see, after the
initial injury,

01:07:31.520 --> 01:07:35.420 align:middle line:84%
I ended up hiking four miles
up a mountain, four miles down

01:07:35.420 --> 01:07:36.800 align:middle line:84%
a mountain, and
another three miles

01:07:36.800 --> 01:07:38.700 align:middle line:84%
into town before
my leg gave out.

01:07:38.700 --> 01:07:42.670 align:middle line:84%
Well, all I can
say is, nice sprain.

01:07:42.670 --> 01:07:44.237 align:middle line:84%
Lose the crutches
when you can and bear

01:07:44.237 --> 01:07:45.270 align:middle line:90%
weight as you feel comfortable.

01:07:45.270 --> 01:07:48.686 align:middle line:90%


01:07:48.686 --> 01:07:51.190 align:middle line:90%
PAM: I was intrigued.

01:07:51.190 --> 01:07:54.520 align:middle line:84%
As quickly as the
questions arose in my mind,

01:07:54.520 --> 01:07:57.915 align:middle line:84%
just as Puma told me,
people and teachers

01:07:57.915 --> 01:07:59.124 align:middle line:90%
began entering my life.

01:07:59.124 --> 01:08:10.990 align:middle line:90%


01:08:10.990 --> 01:08:14.070 align:middle line:84%
I traveled to Mexico and
met healer Maria Teresa

01:08:14.070 --> 01:08:18.700 align:middle line:84%
Valenzuela who had studied with
the experts from NASA's Hubble.

01:08:18.700 --> 01:08:21.970 align:middle line:10%
After giving a scientific-based
analogy of what to expect

01:08:21.970 --> 01:08:26.420 align:middle line:10%
in 2012, merging the indigenous
teachings with science,

01:08:26.420 --> 01:08:29.319 align:middle line:10%
Maria offered a bit of
advice as to what each of us

01:08:29.319 --> 01:08:34.439 align:middle line:10%
can do in preparation for
these upcoming changes.

01:08:34.439 --> 01:08:40.310 align:middle line:84%
We're under this deep, deep
hypnosis for whatever reason.

01:08:40.310 --> 01:08:43.160 align:middle line:90%
But to me, we need to wake up.

01:08:43.160 --> 01:08:44.500 align:middle line:90%
We're running out of time.

01:08:44.500 --> 01:08:47.910 align:middle line:90%
We need to simplify our lives.

01:08:47.910 --> 01:08:51.170 align:middle line:84%
We need to really let
go of a lot of the stuff

01:08:51.170 --> 01:08:56.220 align:middle line:84%
that we run every
weekend to the malls,

01:08:56.220 --> 01:08:58.790 align:middle line:84%
we run to the
supermarkets to buy

01:08:58.790 --> 01:09:02.490 align:middle line:84%
things that sit on the
shelves and collect dust.

01:09:02.490 --> 01:09:06.500 align:middle line:84%
I've seen people that have
these closets full of food

01:09:06.500 --> 01:09:08.450 align:middle line:90%
that they never use.

01:09:08.450 --> 01:09:10.670 align:middle line:84%
We need to let go of our
attachments, things that

01:09:10.670 --> 01:09:12.950 align:middle line:90%
just don't serve us anymore.

01:09:12.950 --> 01:09:15.540 align:middle line:84%
We as human beings need
tremendous healings

01:09:15.540 --> 01:09:17.060 align:middle line:90%
from our addictions.

01:09:17.060 --> 01:09:19.790 align:middle line:84%
And our addiction's in
many, many, many forms.

01:09:19.790 --> 01:09:25.260 align:middle line:84%
I can go to alcohol,
drugs, the television,

01:09:25.260 --> 01:09:27.580 align:middle line:90%
our addictions of privilege.

01:09:27.580 --> 01:09:29.314 align:middle line:90%
That's a big one.

01:09:29.314 --> 01:09:31.810 align:middle line:84%
You know, the sense of
privilege that we're more

01:09:31.810 --> 01:09:33.970 align:middle line:90%
dominant than the other one.

01:09:33.970 --> 01:09:38.090 align:middle line:84%
Our addictions of our
emotions, of our angers.

01:09:38.090 --> 01:09:39.779 align:middle line:84%
They need to get rid
of their credit cards.

01:09:39.779 --> 01:09:42.460 align:middle line:84%
By growing your own
gardens, learning

01:09:42.460 --> 01:09:45.010 align:middle line:84%
to walk lighter in
life, you will not need

01:09:45.010 --> 01:09:48.680 align:middle line:90%
this dense card, this density.

01:09:48.680 --> 01:09:50.080 align:middle line:90%
So I ask, get rid of them.

01:09:50.080 --> 01:09:51.420 align:middle line:90%
Pay up your debts.

01:09:51.420 --> 01:09:53.819 align:middle line:84%
They need to come
into communities.

01:09:53.819 --> 01:09:56.910 align:middle line:84%
OK, working in communities
is very important.

01:09:56.910 --> 01:10:00.210 align:middle line:84%
I see a lot of people that are
very, very lonely in cities.

01:10:00.210 --> 01:10:02.300 align:middle line:90%
They live by themselves.

01:10:02.300 --> 01:10:06.110 align:middle line:84%
So I ask, have you
ever thought of maybe

01:10:06.110 --> 01:10:11.260 align:middle line:84%
finding an empty apartment
house in a group of your friends

01:10:11.260 --> 01:10:14.910 align:middle line:84%
that you really like,
do, like, co-housing?

01:10:14.910 --> 01:10:17.950 align:middle line:84%
And then also, like, if
people live in neighborhoods

01:10:17.950 --> 01:10:21.570 align:middle line:84%
that maybe once a week they
come together as a community

01:10:21.570 --> 01:10:23.470 align:middle line:90%
and they work as a community.

01:10:23.470 --> 01:10:26.630 align:middle line:84%
That's where the
gardens come in.

01:10:26.630 --> 01:10:29.950 align:middle line:84%
And another thing that is
very important in these times

01:10:29.950 --> 01:10:32.360 align:middle line:84%
is that you need to take
care of your bodies.

01:10:32.360 --> 01:10:35.610 align:middle line:84%
As you know, everything
is more polluted.

01:10:35.610 --> 01:10:38.900 align:middle line:84%
And as we move a little bit
forward in these coming years,

01:10:38.900 --> 01:10:40.100 align:middle line:84%
it is said that
everything is going

01:10:40.100 --> 01:10:43.990 align:middle line:84%
to get even more polluted,
and that more death is coming.

01:10:43.990 --> 01:10:48.860 align:middle line:84%
So that each of us needs to
exercise more, eat better,

01:10:48.860 --> 01:10:50.810 align:middle line:90%
do more walking.

01:10:50.810 --> 01:10:53.810 align:middle line:84%
And I can leave you
with this message

01:10:53.810 --> 01:10:56.220 align:middle line:90%
that I truly, truly do believe.

01:10:56.220 --> 01:11:01.280 align:middle line:84%
That there's no reason
to fear the future,

01:11:01.280 --> 01:11:03.450 align:middle line:90%
because we come from the future.

01:11:03.450 --> 01:11:06.020 align:middle line:90%
We come from the stars.

01:11:06.020 --> 01:11:08.730 align:middle line:84%
So there is no
reason to fear it.

01:11:08.730 --> 01:11:11.790 align:middle line:84%
There's wonderful
possibilities up there.

01:11:11.790 --> 01:11:15.500 align:middle line:10%
PAM: I learned about kinesiology
from Sonny Molina, a shaman

01:11:15.500 --> 01:11:18.120 align:middle line:10%
I met who practices sports
medicine at the Sanada

01:11:18.120 --> 01:11:20.600 align:middle line:10%
