can talk to you, giving

01:11:23.800 --> 01:11:26.290 align:middle line:84%
you the answers to
all your questions,

01:11:26.290 --> 01:11:27.690 align:middle line:90%
whether simple or abstract.

01:11:27.690 --> 01:11:31.030 align:middle line:90%


01:11:31.030 --> 01:11:34.180 align:middle line:84%
This was all now
beginning to make sense.

01:11:34.180 --> 01:11:37.200 align:middle line:84%
I started making
changes in my own mind.

01:11:37.200 --> 01:11:39.890 align:middle line:84%
I joined a neighborhood
garden club.

01:11:39.890 --> 01:11:43.030 align:middle line:84%
I started growing
my own vegetables.

01:11:43.030 --> 01:11:47.070 align:middle line:84%
I actually know the
names of my neighbors.

01:11:47.070 --> 01:11:50.690 align:middle line:84%
I excitedly shared by newfound
knowledge with my daughter.

01:11:50.690 --> 01:11:53.510 align:middle line:84%
And with each new
piece of information,

01:11:53.510 --> 01:11:58.560 align:middle line:84%
she began to apply these
tools to her own life.

01:11:58.560 --> 01:12:01.130 align:middle line:10%
Soon after, she got
a good paying job

01:12:01.130 --> 01:12:04.060 align:middle line:10%
and moved into an
apartment with the kids,

01:12:04.060 --> 01:12:07.350 align:middle line:10%
their first real apartment.

01:12:07.350 --> 01:12:08.640 align:middle line:90%
And then the challenges began.

01:12:08.640 --> 01:12:12.700 align:middle line:90%


01:12:12.700 --> 01:12:16.930 align:middle line:84%
