had been released from prison.

01:12:16.930 --> 01:12:19.050 align:middle line:84%
Despite a restraining
order, he continued

01:12:19.050 --> 01:12:21.730 align:middle line:90%
to stalk Ariana and the kids.

01:12:21.730 --> 01:12:24.140 align:middle line:90%
She knew he was using again.

01:12:24.140 --> 01:12:27.960 align:middle line:84%
They had traded text messages
over the past several days.

01:12:27.960 --> 01:12:30.475 align:middle line:84%
